    <item>
      <title>特朗普称关税将为美国带来更多就业机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-13/trump-says-tariffs-will-lead-to-more-jobs-in-us-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统下令其政府考虑对众多贸易伙伴征收互惠关税，以创造公平的竞争环境。特朗普表示，关税将使美国“充满就业机会”，大多数商品的价格最终都会下降。他在椭圆形办公室对记者发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-13/trump-says-tariffs-will-lead-to-more-jobs-in-us-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 20:25:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Google 与 Reddit 的共生关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-13/google-s-symbiotic-relationship-with-reddit-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Reddit 首席运营官 Jen Wong 谈到了谷歌对公司的影响，该公司公布的第四季度收益低于分析师预期。他与 Caroline Hyde 和 Jackie Davalos 一起参加了“彭博科技”节目。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-13/google-s-symbiotic-relationship-with-reddit-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 20:18:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称无需出售公司后美国钢铁股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/us-steel-shares-drop-after-trump-says-no-need-to-sell-company</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他的关税措施正在拯救该公司，同时撇清与日本钢铁制造商新日铁公司进行投资谈判的提议，随后美国钢铁公司股价一度下跌 1.9%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/us-steel-shares-drop-after-trump-says-no-need-to-sell-company</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 20:07:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普要求欧洲购买美国武器以保持北约强大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-tells-europe-to-buy-american-weapons-to-keep-nato-strong</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情的欧洲官员透露，特朗普总统的政府已告诉英国和欧洲的盟友，希望他们购买美国武器和军事装备，以维护北约联盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-tells-europe-to-buy-american-weapons-to-keep-nato-strong</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 19:05:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利在强劲需求下增加最新 X 债券发行量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/morgan-stanley-aims-to-boost-size-of-latest-x-debt-offering</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利 (Morgan Stanley) 将最新发行的 X Holdings Corp. 债券的规模增至 47.4 亿美元，使该公司和其他贷款机构有望最终摆脱他们为伊隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 2022 年收购该社交媒体平台安排的融资中的大部分风险敞口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/morgan-stanley-aims-to-boost-size-of-latest-x-debt-offering</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 15:35:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普宣布征收关税，暗示美国通胀温和，债券价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/us-bonds-rise-after-hot-inflation-fuels-worst-day-since-december</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受唐纳德·特朗普最新关税承诺的影响，美国国债价格上涨，延续了此前的涨势。此前发布的生产者物价报告显示，周三因消费者通胀数据过热而引发的抛售被夸大了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/us-bonds-rise-after-hot-inflation-fuels-worst-day-since-december</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 10:59:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称各国将面临互惠关税，美元下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/dollar-falls-as-trump-putin-talk-over-end-to-war-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们考虑特朗普总统计划对与美国有贸易往来的国家征收互惠关税的影响，美元跌至盘中低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/dollar-falls-as-trump-putin-talk-over-end-to-war-in-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 05:03:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税延迟抵消俄罗斯出口风险下降，油价企稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价收盘基本持平，从去年 12 月以来的最低点反弹，因美国总统唐纳德·特朗普实施对等关税的计划时间不明朗，抵消了俄罗斯供应可能缓解的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 23:35:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：标普 500 指数上涨 1%，因关税推迟导致美元下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普决定对等征收关税，但不会立即实施，股市延续涨势，美元则受到冲击。黄金价格创下新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 22:26:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
